{{Infobox hieroglyphs two-columns
|NAME-ERWEITERT = {{ill|New Kingdom of Egypt|de|Neues Reich|qq=draft}}
|NAME = <hiero>S29-Aa17-V28-D61-N14:N35</hiero><br/>Seba-en-Sah<br /> ''Sb3-n-S3ḥ'' <br/> ''Star of the Descending One (Toe or Foot Star)'' 
|BILD1 = Orion-Sternkarte.png 
